data.description: This all-brick home sitting on 6 acres is just waiting for you! Remodeled with the main living area ceiling raised to be a cathedral, the plumbing, wiring and roof were all replaced, plus new storm windows. Living area is open to the eat-in kitchen complete with a breakfast bar, pantry and a natural gas cookstove. Beautiful mature trees abound on the property and there is plenty of room for horse pens. Several outbuildings include a 35 x 40 insulated shop that has a new overhead door along with lean-to's and an 11 x 14 office or hobby space with a 1/2 bath and 10 x 12 covered area for entertaining. Above ground 16 x 32 soft swim pool with deck. Horse barn with a nice tack room and corral. You can literally walk across the street to the new WOKA walking trail.
